title: Favorite social networks of U.S. teens 2012 to 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 13 different Responses for 8 groups Snapchat, Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, Tumblr, Pinterest, Google+, and Other that are presented on the X-axis.
Response Fall 2017 had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 8 groups, and it was for Snapchat. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Response Fall 2012 for Snapchat.
In Response Fall 2012, Google+ had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Response Spring 2017 out of all 13 Responses.
There is a gap of 6.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for Google+ in Response Fall 2012 and Spring 2017.
